7.3 DUIM-Layouts Module

table-contents

Generic function

Summary

Returns the contents of the specified table.

Signature

table-contents table => contents

Arguments

table
An instance of type <table-layout>.

Values

contents
An instance of type <sheet>.

Library

duim-layouts

Module

duim-layouts

Description

Returns the contents of table.

See also

table-contents-setter, page 494
